{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1042,"text":"My seven-year-old grandson\nsleeps just down the hall from me,"},{"time":4544,"text":"and he wakes up a lot of mornings"},{"time":6234,"text":"and he says,"},{"time":7796,"text":"\"You know, this could be\nthe best day ever.\""},{"time":10565,"text":"And other times,\nin the middle of the night,"},{"time":12766,"text":"he calls out in a tremulous voice,"},{"time":15716,"text":"\"Nana, will you ever get sick and die?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":19198,"text":"I think this pretty much says it for me\nand most of the people I know,"},{"time":23664,"text":"that we're a mixed grill\nof happy anticipation"},{"time":26968,"text":"and dread."},{"time":28580,"text":"So I sat down a few days\nbefore my 61st birthday,"},{"time":32826,"text":"and I decided to compile a list\nof everything I know for sure."},{"time":38017,"text":"There's so little truth\nin the popular culture,"},{"time":41164,"text":"and it's good to be sure of a few things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":45217,"text":"For instance, I am no longer 47,"},{"time":48845,"text":"although this is the age I feel,"},{"time":51649,"text":"and the age I like to think\nof myself as being."},{"time":54854,"text":"My friend Paul used to say in his late 70s"},{"time":57551,"text":"that he felt like a young man\nwith something really wrong with him."}]},{"cues":[{"time":61158,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":65032,"text":"Our true person is outside\nof time and space,"},{"time":67896,"text":"but looking at the paperwork,"},{"time":69430,"text":"I can, in fact, see\nthat I was born in 1954."},{"time":73353,"text":"My inside self is outside\nof time and space."},{"time":76329,"text":"It doesn't have an age."},{"time":78398,"text":"I'm every age I've ever been,\nand so are you,"},{"time":81771,"text":"although I can't help\nmentioning as an aside"},{"time":84479,"text":"that it might have been helpful\nif I hadn't followed"},{"time":87134,"text":"the skin care rules of the '60s,"},{"time":89679,"text":"which involved getting\nas much sun as possible"},{"time":93097,"text":"while slathered in baby oil"},{"time":95667,"text":"and basking in the glow\nof a tinfoil reflector shield."}]},{"cues":[{"time":99938,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":101676,"text":"It was so liberating, though,\nto face the truth"},{"time":104298,"text":"that I was no longer\nin the last throes of middle age,"},{"time":107670,"text":"that I decided to write down\nevery single true thing I know."},{"time":112046,"text":"People feel really doomed\nand overwhelmed these days,"},{"time":115468,"text":"and they keep asking me what's true."},{"time":118214,"text":"So I hope that my list of things\nI'm almost positive about"},{"time":124587,"text":"might offer some basic\noperating instructions"},{"time":127676,"text":"to anyone who is feeling\nreally overwhelmed or beleaguered."}]},{"cues":[{"time":132140,"text":"Number one:"},{"time":134046,"text":"the first and truest thing\nis that all truth is a paradox."},{"time":137731,"text":"Life is both a precious,\nunfathomably beautiful gift,"},{"time":142070,"text":"and it's impossible here,\non the incarnational side of things."},{"time":146776,"text":"It's been a very bad match"},{"time":148420,"text":"for those of us who were born\nextremely sensitive."},{"time":151710,"text":"It's so hard and weird\nthat we sometimes wonder"},{"time":154598,"text":"if we're being punked."},{"time":157002,"text":"It's filled simultaneously\nwith heartbreaking sweetness and beauty,"},{"time":161980,"text":"desperate poverty,"},{"time":163779,"text":"floods and babies and acne and Mozart,"},{"time":167347,"text":"all swirled together."},{"time":169510,"text":"I don't think it's an ideal system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":172104,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":175444,"text":"Number two: almost\neverything will work again"},{"time":178863,"text":"if you unplug it for a few minutes --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":181228,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":183947,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":187253,"text":"including you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":190975,"text":"Three: there is almost\nnothing outside of you"},{"time":194237,"text":"that will help in any kind of lasting way,"},{"time":197173,"text":"unless you're waiting for an organ."},{"time":199958,"text":"You can't buy, achieve or date\nserenity and peace of mind."},{"time":204920,"text":"This is the most horrible truth,\nand I so resent it."},{"time":209549,"text":"But it's an inside job,"},{"time":211797,"text":"and we can't arrange peace\nor lasting improvement"},{"time":214639,"text":"for the people we love most in the world."},{"time":217051,"text":"They have to find their own ways,"},{"time":219155,"text":"their own answers."},{"time":220801,"text":"You can't run alongside\nyour grown children"},{"time":224452,"text":"with sunscreen and ChapStick\non their hero's journey."},{"time":229062,"text":"You have to release them."},{"time":231203,"text":"It's disrespectful not to."},{"time":235088,"text":"And if it's someone else's problem,"},{"time":236971,"text":"you probably don't have\nthe answer, anyway."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239295,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":240511,"text":"Our help is usually not very helpful."},{"time":243748,"text":"Our help is often toxic."},{"time":246824,"text":"And help is the sunny side of control."},{"time":250836,"text":"Stop helping so much."},{"time":253334,"text":"Don't get your help and goodness\nall over everybody."}]},{"cues":[{"time":256815,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":259351,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":261036,"text":"This brings us to number four:"},{"time":263033,"text":"everyone is screwed up,\nbroken, clingy and scared,"},{"time":266941,"text":"even the people who seem\nto have it most together."},{"time":269940,"text":"They are much more like you\nthan you would believe,"},{"time":272403,"text":"so try not to compare your insides\nto other people's outsides."},{"time":277075,"text":"It will only make you worse\nthan you already are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279965,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":284272,"text":"Also, you can't save, fix\nor rescue any of them"},{"time":287767,"text":"or get anyone sober."},{"time":289826,"text":"What helped me get clean\nand sober 30 years ago"},{"time":292604,"text":"was the catastrophe\nof my behavior and thinking."},{"time":296239,"text":"So I asked some sober friends for help,"},{"time":298269,"text":"and I turned to a higher power."},{"time":300227,"text":"One acronym for God\nis the \"gift of desperation,\""},{"time":304310,"text":"G-O-D,"},{"time":305763,"text":"or as a sober friend put it,"},{"time":307819,"text":"by the end I was deteriorating faster\nthan I could lower my standards."}]},{"cues":[{"time":312810,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":319145,"text":"So God might mean, in this case,"},{"time":321479,"text":"\"me running out of any more good ideas.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":325532,"text":"While fixing and saving\nand trying to rescue is futile,"},{"time":329722,"text":"radical self-care is quantum,"},{"time":333157,"text":"and it radiates out from you\ninto the atmosphere"},{"time":336797,"text":"like a little fresh air."},{"time":338466,"text":"It's a huge gift to the world."},{"time":341071,"text":"When people respond by saying,\n\"Well, isn't she full of herself,\""},{"time":345605,"text":"just smile obliquely like Mona Lisa"},{"time":348595,"text":"and make both of you a nice cup of tea."},{"time":352605,"text":"Being full of affection\nfor one's goofy, self-centered,"},{"time":357312,"text":"cranky, annoying self"},{"time":359829,"text":"is home."},{"time":361382,"text":"It's where world peace begins."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365038,"text":"Number five:"},{"time":366779,"text":"chocolate with 75 percent cacao\nis not actually a food."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371867,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":375903,"text":"Its best use is as a bait in snake traps"},{"time":380007,"text":"or to balance the legs of wobbly chairs."},{"time":384591,"text":"It was never meant\nto be considered an edible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":389865,"text":"Number six --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":391254,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":394782,"text":"writing."},{"time":396874,"text":"Every writer you know writes\nreally terrible first drafts,"},{"time":401286,"text":"but they keep their butt in the chair."},{"time":403463,"text":"That's the secret of life."},{"time":405207,"text":"That's probably the main difference\nbetween you and them."},{"time":408431,"text":"They just do it."},{"time":409917,"text":"They do it by prearrangement\nwith themselves."},{"time":412507,"text":"They do it as a debt of honor."},{"time":415336,"text":"They tell stories that come through them"},{"time":417654,"text":"one day at a time, little by little."},{"time":420188,"text":"When my older brother was in fourth grade,"},{"time":422438,"text":"he had a term paper on birds\ndue the next day,"},{"time":426436,"text":"and he hadn't started."},{"time":428740,"text":"So my dad sat down with him\nwith an Audubon book,"},{"time":432846,"text":"paper, pencils and brads --"},{"time":435214,"text":"for those of you who have gotten\na little less young and remember brads --"},{"time":440838,"text":"and he said to my brother,"},{"time":443692,"text":"\"Just take it bird by bird, buddy."},{"time":446326,"text":"Just read about pelicans"},{"time":448665,"text":"and then write about pelicans\nin your own voice."},{"time":452545,"text":"And then find out about chickadees,"},{"time":455724,"text":"and tell us about them in your own voice."},{"time":458519,"text":"And then geese.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":460289,"text":"So the two most important things\nabout writing are: bird by bird"},{"time":464061,"text":"and really god-awful first drafts."},{"time":467959,"text":"If you don't know where to start,"},{"time":469658,"text":"remember that every single thing\nthat happened to you is yours,"},{"time":472911,"text":"and you get to tell it."},{"time":474852,"text":"If people wanted you to write\nmore warmly about them,"},{"time":478038,"text":"they should've behaved better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":479782,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":482836,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":487145,"text":"You're going to feel like hell\nif you wake up someday"},{"time":490042,"text":"and you never wrote the stuff"},{"time":491827,"text":"that is tugging on the sleeves\nof your heart:"},{"time":495312,"text":"your stories, memories,\nvisions and songs --"},{"time":498732,"text":"your truth,"},{"time":500409,"text":"your version of things --"},{"time":502258,"text":"in your own voice."},{"time":503767,"text":"That's really all you have to offer us,"},{"time":506266,"text":"and that's also why you were born."}]},{"cues":[{"time":510488,"text":"Seven: publication and temporary\ncreative successes"},{"time":514697,"text":"are something you have to recover from."},{"time":517744,"text":"They kill as many people as not."},{"time":520610,"text":"They will hurt, damage and change you"},{"time":523164,"text":"in ways you cannot imagine."},{"time":525707,"text":"The most degraded\nand evil people I've ever known"},{"time":529247,"text":"are male writers who've had\nhuge best sellers."},{"time":533093,"text":"And yet, returning to number one,\nthat all truth is paradox,"},{"time":537274,"text":"it's also a miracle\nto get your work published,"},{"time":539723,"text":"to get your stories read and heard."},{"time":542583,"text":"Just try to bust yourself\ngently of the fantasy"},{"time":545362,"text":"that publication will heal you,"},{"time":547840,"text":"that it will fill the Swiss-cheesy\nholes inside of you."},{"time":551948,"text":"It can't."},{"time":553566,"text":"It won't."},{"time":554950,"text":"But writing can."},{"time":556679,"text":"So can singing in a choir\nor a bluegrass band."},{"time":560301,"text":"So can painting community\nmurals or birding"},{"time":563632,"text":"or fostering old dogs\nthat no one else will."}]},{"cues":[{"time":568570,"text":"Number eight: families."},{"time":572883,"text":"Families are hard, hard, hard,"},{"time":576003,"text":"no matter how cherished\nand astonishing they may also be."},{"time":579453,"text":"Again, see number one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":581603,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":582674,"text":"At family gatherings where you suddenly\nfeel homicidal or suicidal --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":586986,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":588026,"text":"remember that in all cases,"},{"time":590381,"text":"it's a miracle that any of us,\nspecifically, were conceived and born."},{"time":596520,"text":"Earth is forgiveness school."},{"time":598471,"text":"It begins with forgiving yourself,"},{"time":600605,"text":"and then you might as well\nstart at the dinner table."},{"time":604640,"text":"That way, you can do this work\nin comfortable pants."}]},{"cues":[{"time":608309,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":611279,"text":"When William Blake said that we are here"},{"time":613250,"text":"to learn to endure the beams of love,"},{"time":616262,"text":"he knew that your family would be\nan intimate part of this,"},{"time":619619,"text":"even as you want to run screaming\nfor your cute little life."},{"time":623811,"text":"But I promise you are up to it."},{"time":626394,"text":"You can do it, Cinderella, you can do it,"},{"time":629798,"text":"and you will be amazed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":633164,"text":"Nine: food."},{"time":636187,"text":"Try to do a little better."},{"time":639497,"text":"I think you know what I mean."}]},{"cues":[{"time":641411,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":651159,"text":"Number 10 --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":652334,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":654582,"text":"grace."},{"time":656428,"text":"Grace is spiritual WD-40,"},{"time":659559,"text":"or water wings."},{"time":661063,"text":"The mystery of grace is that God loves\nHenry Kissinger and Vladimir Putin"},{"time":667054,"text":"and me"},{"time":668237,"text":"exactly as much as He or She\nloves your new grandchild."},{"time":672988,"text":"Go figure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":674229,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":676030,"text":"The movement of grace\nis what changes us, heals us"},{"time":679391,"text":"and heals our world."},{"time":681413,"text":"To summon grace, say, \"Help,\"\nand then buckle up."},{"time":685208,"text":"Grace finds you exactly where you are,"},{"time":687922,"text":"but it doesn't leave you\nwhere it found you."},{"time":690471,"text":"And grace won't look\nlike Casper the Friendly Ghost,"},{"time":693591,"text":"regrettably."},{"time":695220,"text":"But the phone will ring\nor the mail will come"},{"time":697627,"text":"and then against all odds,"},{"time":699131,"text":"you'll get your sense of humor\nabout yourself back."},{"time":702571,"text":"Laughter really is carbonated holiness."},{"time":706874,"text":"It helps us breathe again and again"},{"time":709590,"text":"and gives us back to ourselves,"},{"time":711747,"text":"and this gives us faith\nin life and each other."},{"time":716495,"text":"And remember -- grace always bats last."}]},{"cues":[{"time":721652,"text":"Eleven: God just means goodness."},{"time":724785,"text":"It's really not all that scary."},{"time":727250,"text":"It means the divine or a loving,\nanimating intelligence,"},{"time":731724,"text":"or, as we learned\nfrom the great \"Deteriorata,\""},{"time":735473,"text":"\"the cosmic muffin.\""},{"time":737800,"text":"A good name for God is: \"Not me.\""},{"time":741827,"text":"Emerson said that\nthe happiest person on Earth"},{"time":744597,"text":"is the one who learns from nature\nthe lessons of worship."},{"time":748799,"text":"So go outside a lot and look up."},{"time":751949,"text":"My pastor said you can trap bees\non the bottom of mason jars without lids"},{"time":756476,"text":"because they don't look up,"},{"time":758213,"text":"so they just walk around bitterly\nbumping into the glass walls."},{"time":762637,"text":"Go outside. Look up."},{"time":765029,"text":"Secret of life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":767477,"text":"And finally: death."},{"time":770373,"text":"Number 12."},{"time":772646,"text":"Wow and yikes."},{"time":775375,"text":"It's so hard to bear when the few people\nyou cannot live without die."},{"time":779624,"text":"You'll never get over these losses,\nand no matter what the culture says,"},{"time":783285,"text":"you're not supposed to."},{"time":785176,"text":"We Christians like to think of death\nas a major change of address,"},{"time":790343,"text":"but in any case, the person\nwill live again fully in your heart"},{"time":794953,"text":"if you don't seal it off."},{"time":796969,"text":"Like Leonard Cohen said,\n\"There are cracks in everything,"},{"time":799761,"text":"and that's how the light gets in.\""},{"time":801638,"text":"And that's how we feel\nour people again fully alive."}]},{"cues":[{"time":807240,"text":"Also, the people will make\nyou laugh out loud"},{"time":811275,"text":"at the most inconvenient times,"},{"time":814365,"text":"and that's the great good news."},{"time":816463,"text":"But their absence will also be a lifelong\nnightmare of homesickness for you."},{"time":820942,"text":"Grief and friends, time and tears\nwill heal you to some extent."},{"time":825647,"text":"Tears will bathe and baptize\nand hydrate and moisturize you"},{"time":829922,"text":"and the ground on which you walk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":832275,"text":"Do you know the first thing\nthat God says to Moses?"},{"time":836028,"text":"He says, \"Take off your shoes.\""},{"time":839079,"text":"Because this is holy ground,\nall evidence to the contrary."},{"time":843143,"text":"It's hard to believe,\nbut it's the truest thing I know."},{"time":846232,"text":"When you're a little bit older,\nlike my tiny personal self,"},{"time":850398,"text":"you realize that death\nis as sacred as birth."},{"time":854785,"text":"And don't worry -- get on with your life."},{"time":858405,"text":"Almost every single death\nis easy and gentle"},{"time":862924,"text":"with the very best people surrounding you"},{"time":865964,"text":"for as long as you need."},{"time":867831,"text":"You won't be alone."},{"time":870686,"text":"They'll help you cross over\nto whatever awaits us."},{"time":874871,"text":"As Ram Dass said,"},{"time":876632,"text":"\"When all is said and done,"},{"time":878516,"text":"we're really just all walking\neach other home.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":883024,"text":"I think that's it,"},{"time":884636,"text":"but if I think of anything else,"},{"time":886762,"text":"I'll let you know."}]},{"cues":[{"time":888248,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":889475,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":891078,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":892378,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":894210,"text":"I was very surprised to be asked to come,"},{"time":896388,"text":"because it is not my realm,"},{"time":899095,"text":"technology or design or entertainment."},{"time":901446,"text":"I mean, my realm is sort of\nfaith and writing"},{"time":904651,"text":"and kind of lurching along together."},{"time":907625,"text":"And I was surprised,"},{"time":909412,"text":"but they said I could give a talk,\nand I said I'd love to."}]},{"cues":[{"time":913709,"text":"(Video) If you don't know where to start,"},{"time":915785,"text":"remember that every single thing\nthat happened to you is yours"},{"time":918934,"text":"and you get to tell it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":920336,"text":"Anne Lamott: People are very frightened\nand feel really doomed"},{"time":923465,"text":"in America these days,"},{"time":924677,"text":"and I just wanted to help people\nget their sense of humor about it"},{"time":927842,"text":"and to realize how much isn't a problem."},{"time":931464,"text":"If you take an action,"},{"time":935539,"text":"take a really healthy or loving\nor friendly action,"},{"time":939126,"text":"you'll have loving and friendly feelings."}]}]}